    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014garage-kept, pampered, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every inch is absolutely pristine, and the engine purrs like a kitten. It\u2019s a rare find in this kind of shape, and I\u2019ve made sure it\u2019s lived a very charmed life. Come take a look, and I promise you\u2019ll fall in love just like I did!",
