    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a masterfully sorted E46 M3, a true icon of the analog era. This S54 powerplant is in peak mechanical health, featuring a fully overhauled VANOS system with upgraded seals and a precision valve adjustment to ensure optimal volumetric efficiency across the entire 8,000 RPM sweep. The chassis integrity is unparalleled; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with a structural plate kit to mitigate any fatigue under high-torque loads. Power is delivered through a crisp, short-throw 6-speed manual to a lock-tight helical LSD. The suspension geometry has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings for laser-sharp turn-in and zero deflection. Finished in a deep, high-gloss coat with impeccable depth, the interior remains a time capsule with zero bolster fatigue or dash delamination. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
